    <div class="post-body">
        
            <p><center><iframe src="//player.vimeo.com/video/83976926" frameborder="0" width="590" height="332" allowfullscreen=""></iframe>
</center></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: xx-small;"><a href="http://vimeo.com/83976926">Art Project 2023</a> from <a href="http://vimeo.com/user6029937">Enxuto &amp; Love</a> on <a href="https://vimeo.com">Vimeo</a></span>.</p>

<div id="magicdomid2067" class="ace-line"><em>This is Rhizome Today for Friday, August 29, 2014</em></div>
<div id="magicdomid2068" class="ace-line"> </div>
<div id="magicdomid2069" class="ace-line"><em>Rhizome Today is an experiment in ephemeral blogging: a series of posts that are written hastily in response to current events, and disappeared within a day or so. At the end of each month, we'll republish highlights from the series in a more selective and polished form. The latest post can always be found at </em><a href="http://www.rhizome.org/today"><em>http://www.rhizome.org/today</em></a><em>.</em></div>
            
                
